acceptance_criteria[8]: Timer home screen with large start/stop button and elapsed time display,Break timer with configurable short/long break durations,"Pomodoro mode: 25min work / 5min break cycle with session counter",Timer report screen with daily/weekly/monthly chart views,Active timer persists across app backgrounding,"API endpoints: POST /api/timers/start, POST /api/timers/stop, GET /api/timers/current, GET /api/timers/reports?period=weekly",Timer state synced with server in real-time via WebSocket,Export report option (share as PDF or CSV)